CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 1, 1955, pg. 9, reads: "North Side, Suburban Ushers - The North Side and Suburban Ushers Alliances distributed all of these bags of food and many other items to needy families at Christmas time.  They do similar work throughout the year. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of North Side and Suburban Ushers Alliance posed behind bags of food, in interior with columns and pressed tin ceiling
